# Dismissal Firmware Public Key (Ed25519, raw 32 bytes, base64)
# This is an EXAMPLE file — the real production key lives at
# /opt/dismissal/keys/firmware.pub on each Pi and is generated via:
#   python deploy/sign_firmware.py gen-keypair --out-dir ./fw-keys
#
# Verification (Backend/dismissal_ota_verify.py) ignores comment lines
# starting with `#` and decodes the remaining base64 as the raw key.
# Replace the line below with your generated public key before shipping.
AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA=
